# Travel Photography Gallery

This directory should contain your travel photography collection.

## Required Images:
Add 6 or more images named:
- travel-1.jpg
- travel-2.jpg
- travel-3.jpg
- travel-4.jpg
- travel-5.jpg
- travel-6.jpg
- (continue numbering as needed)

## Specifications:
- Dimensions: 1200x1600px or higher (3:4 aspect ratio / portrait)
- Format: JPG (optimized for web, under 300KB each recommended)
- Content: Your best travel photography - landscapes, cultures, architecture, people, places

## How to Add:
1. Select your best travel photographs
2. Rename them following the numbering pattern (travel-1.jpg, travel-2.jpg, etc.)
3. Place them in `/public/photos/travel/`
4. If adding more than 6, also update `/app/portfolio/[category]/page.tsx` to include additional photo entries

The gallery will display these in a responsive 3-column grid on desktop, 2 columns on tablet, and 1 column on mobile.
